@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### GATEKEEPER MODULE - Access Control
### ============================================

### ROLES - Check Permission
GET {{baseUrl}}/gatekeeper/check-permission?action=read&resource=contact&resourceId=uuid
Authorization: {{token}}

### ROLES - Get User Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/gatekeeper/permissions
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Returns 403 if user lacks permission
